The paper proposes and implements a general distributed data storage system, which involves designing a data structure similar to Git, synthesizing designs from distributed systems and databases, and evaluating four applications on top of the storage. Therefore, the paper is likely to belong to the Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing (cs.DC), Databases (cs.DB), Data Structures and Algorithms (cs.DS), Software Engineering (cs.SE), and Cryptography and Security (cs.CR) sub-categories.
